{"tid":1141362,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"中國市場對日本動畫業界的影響力，《邪神與廚二病少女》2期要先等中國審批才放送","createTime":"2019-05-06T12:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T02:32:59.000Z","uid":75050,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6023322e024b5c7d08153ff12f6b5b5d1eec6bc2","tid":1141362,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:18:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/85771/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F85771%2F&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHvrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=6739ec40\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/85771/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/00-20.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F00-20.jpg%3F&h=c84b7a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國市場對日本動畫業界的影響力，《邪神與廚二病少女》2期要先等中國審批才放送</strong><br />\n<br />\n作者: 填海紳士 日期: 05/05/2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/%E9%82%AA%E7%A5%9E%E8%88%87%E5%BB%9A%E4%BA%8C%E7%97%85%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F%25E9%2582%25AA%25E7%25A5%259E%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25BB%259A%25E4%25BA%258C%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3.jpg%3F&h=3826106a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說到《邪神與廚二病少女》這部2018年的7月夏番，當時官方為了製作動畫第2期，可謂是拚命推銷光碟<br />\n<br />\n在歷盡千辛萬苦後，動畫光碟終於賣夠2000(記憶中好像還不是卷均2000而是上下BOX合計2000)<br />\n<br />\n到2019年1月終於宣佈《邪神與廚二病少女》動畫第2期製作決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/77896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F77896&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHvrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=1b9023eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/77896</a><br />\n<br />\n而最近在一場《邪神與廚二病少女》的線下舞台活動中，製作人就提到有關動畫第2期的製作進度<br />\n<br />\n在製作人透露的情報中，有一件事情讓日本網友們相當在意<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-12.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F01-12.jpg%3F&h=962fa59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那就是為了在全世界同步公開，動畫第2期要先等中國有關當局進行檢閱<br />\n<br />\n雖然動畫製作進度順利，但要在中國正版放送，就要在製作完成所有話數後做審批<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/%E9%82%AA%E7%A5%9E%E8%88%87%E5%BB%9A%E4%BA%8C%E7%97%85%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F%25E9%2582%25AA%25E7%25A5%259E%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25BB%259A%25E4%25BA%258C%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3.jpg%3F&h=c3e3d1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自中國市場對日本動畫業界構成的影響力又一顯著例證(茶"},{"pid":"f6d27800336ce16bf77f0e51a43d458388eec6b6","tid":1141362,"uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"呢套只係開始，以後好多新番都要送支國審批先播得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f469e22dc4461e1bdf6c6040ceaf57dce213193a","tid":1141362,"uid":95452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"呢套本身都窮開，僅僅過二千先出到第二季，可能真係等住中國資金先有錢畫"},{"pid":"e81563ca7e216f34023681768dd3482848212942","tid":1141362,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f469e22dc4461e1bdf6c6040ceaf57dce213193a","tid":1141362,"uid":95452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"呢套本身都窮開，僅僅過二千先出到第二季，可能真係等住中國資金先有錢畫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QY3XufR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQY3XufR.png&h=95e83168&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19f5a2647e1da7cb4f67ee3e5d6b7f21316ae946","tid":1141362,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T1